ZH: 1. 为了达成目标，他不遗余力地努力工作。
EN: He works tirelessly to achieve his goals.
ZH: 2. 她不遗余力地帮助他人，总是尽力回报社会。
EN: She spares no effort in helping others and always strives to give back to society.
ZH: 3. 这位教练每天都不遗余力地训练他的运动员。
EN: The coach trains his athletes tirelessly every day.
ZH: 4. 她在公司工作时总是不遗余力地提出改进方案。
EN: She always goes above and beyond to propose improvement plans while working at the company.
ZH: 5. 他是一个不遗余力地照顾家人的人。
EN: He is someone who spares no effort in taking care of his family.
ZH: 6. 这位志愿者每周都不遗余力地为孤寡老人提供帮助。
EN: The volunteer goes all out every week to help the elderly who are alone.
ZH: 7. 他不遗余力地准备考试，期望取得好成绩。
EN: He prepares for the exam meticulously, hoping to achieve good results.
ZH: 8. 她在工作中从不拖延，总是不遗余力地完成任务。
EN: She never procrastinates at work and always goes the extra mile to complete tasks.
ZH: 9. 在战斗中，他们不遗余力地保护彼此。
EN: They protect each other tirelessly in battle.
ZH: 10. 这位导演不遗余力地投入到电影制作中，力求做出最好的作品。
EN: The director throws himself into film production and spares no effort to make the best work.
ZH: 11. 为了实现梦想，他不遗余力地努力学习。
EN: He works hard to study and spare no effort to achieve his dreams.
ZH: 12. 面对困难，他总是不遗余力地坚持下去。
EN: He always perseveres and never spares any effort in the face of difficulties.
ZH: 13. 他不遗余力地奋斗，追求卓越。
EN: He spares no effort in striving for excellence.
ZH: 14. 这个项目需要所有人都不遗余力地合作才能成功。
EN: This project requires everyone to work together tirelessly for it to succeed.
ZH: 15. 他用心灵深处的热情不遗余力地创作音乐。
EN: He creates music with the passion from the depths of his soul without sparing any effort.
ZH: 16. 她是一位不遗余力地关心弱势群体的社工。
EN: She is a social worker who cares tirelessly for vulnerable groups.
ZH: 17. 这位教师用心不遗余力地辅导学生，希望他们取得优异成绩。
EN: The teacher guides the students with dedication and spares no effort, hoping that they will achieve outstanding results.
ZH: 18. 在赈灾活动中，大家都不遗余力地帮助需要帮助的人们。
EN: Everyone helps those in need tirelessly in disaster relief activities.
ZH: 19. 为了实现旅行的愿望，他为获取资金不遗余力地工作。
EN: He works tirelessly to raise funds in order to fulfill his travel dreams.
ZH: 20. 在演出期间，他不遗余力地表演，希望能给观众带来最好的演出。
EN: During the performance, he spares no effort in his acting, hoping to give the audience the best show.
